General.Name: ToTheMoon
General.Description:
ToTheMoon is a full-service mining solution provider. ToTheMoon offers turnkey mining services or custom packages tailored to clients’ needs: full range of mining services from hosting, maintenance and repair to private blockchain servicing. The Partner offers equipment sales through ToTheMoon’s web site.

The MTX is an Ethereum-based token that allows users to interact with the platform. Bounties are paid in MTX on the platform.

Team:

The ToTheMoon Pre-Sale started on the 5th of September. 

The ToTheMoon ICO will take place on the 20th of September, 2017, and will last for 41 days or until the 45,000,000 tokens are sold. During the campaign, 85% of the total TMT supply will be available for purchase at a 0.6-1.1 USD price.
